# Track ONLY the slide research/update task definitions (each folder's SKILL.md).
# Everything else under Scheduled/ (personal digests, generated output,
# the separately-versioned Courses repo, sample data) stays untracked.

# 1. Ignore everything at the top level by default.
/*

# 2. Re-include the slide task folders and this gitignore.
!slide-research-cs6035/
!slide-research-cs6264/
!slide-update-all/
!.gitignore

# 3. Inside those folders, ignore everything except the SKILL.md definition.
slide-research-cs6035/*
!slide-research-cs6035/SKILL.md
slide-research-cs6264/*
!slide-research-cs6264/SKILL.md
slide-update-all/*
!slide-update-all/SKILL.md
